rows.label: qst202606_msg0002
rows.name: You have got to be joking...

rows.label: qst202606_msg0003
rows.name:
It appears Queen Lagert was right.
There are an irregular number of
them here.

rows.label: qst202606_msg0004
rows.name:
Even for the great Zekenator,
this is kind of a tall order...

rows.label: qst202606_msg0005
rows.name:
But we can't leave them like this.
We can't just let them run rampant
all over the world!

rows.label: qst202606_msg0006
rows.name:
With you there, chum. It's time we
nipped this in the bud.

rows.label: qst202606_msg0007
rows.name:
All right, then... Let's go!
Ten'i, back me up!
